[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     13[0m:[38;5;10m[49m This is a strong, well-researched recipe that tackles one of the most studied and most difficult RL applications in healthcare with appropriate intellectual honesty. The RL formulation follows established literature (Komorowski et al., 2018), the safety constraint layer is clinically reasonable, the offline evaluation methodology is correctly framed with appropriate caveats, and the "Honest Take" is genuinely honest about the gap between research promise and clinical deployment. The regulatory discussion (FDA, IRB) is present and appropriately cautious.
